sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Test as Pytest
    participant Factory as FactoryBoy
    participant Mock as PytestMock
    participant App as Application Logic

    Dev->>Test: Run pytest
    Test->>Factory: Request dummy data (e.g. DocumentChunk)
    Factory-->>Test: Return generated object
    Test->>Mock: Mock external dependencies (e.g. ChromaDB)
    Mock-->>Test: Mock object ready
    Test->>App: Execute unit test with mocks/factories
    App-->>Test: Return result
    Test->>Dev: Report Pass/Fail
